Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=8}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A-A snake! - OG}É-É uma cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is this...? - OG}Será que isso é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:58.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Kalgara! Olha isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:04.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a shock! I didn't know that snake had a grandchild... - OG}Que surpresa! Aquela cobra\Ndeve ter tido um neto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Aquela cobra"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A snake, huh? - OG}Cobra, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those two make no sense... - OG}Eu não entendo esses dois...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:20.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles estavam tentando se matar\Naté pouco tempo atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, they're such good friends! - OG}mas agora, são\Npraticamente inseparáveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:26.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kalgara is never very friendly with any of the villagers, either. - OG}Kalgara nem é tão amigável\Nassim com os outros aldeões.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen him smile like that before... - OG}Eu nunca vi ele sorrir\Nassim antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Apenas me siga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We climb down here. - OG}Vamos descer por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Descer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse som...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Kalgara! De onde vem\Nesse lindo som?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me siga e você vai ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui estão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ficou sem palavras?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is Shandia, a city of gold. - OG}Esta é Shandora, a Cidade do Ouro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We are its survivors! - OG}Nós somos o que restou do seu povo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma cidade de ouro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É como se eu estivesse sonhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{W-Whoa! It's gold everywhere! - OG}U-Uau! É tudo de ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:58.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma cidade de tesouros!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, guys! Stop! - OG}E-Ei, pessoal! Calma aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:08.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Load your ship with all the treasure\Nyou can, aside from the gold bell! - OG}Encham o navio com todo o tesouro\Nque quiserem, menos o sino dourado!
Comment: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Load your ship with all the treasure you can, aside from the gold bell!
Comment: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Load your ship with all the treasure you can, aside from the gold bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The villagers already agreed to it. - OG}Nós aldeões não vamos\Naceitar uma recusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:16.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devemos isso a vocês por salvar\Nnossa tribo daquela terrível doença.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is nothing at all. - OG}É o mínimo que podemos fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é muito generoso, Grande Guerreiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:26.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas o seu povo não esteve protegendo\Na cidade todo esse tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes. - OG}De fato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've protected the city, but... - OG}Nós protegemos a cidade, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{not necessarily its treasure! - OG}{not necessarily because of the gold! - Nikki/Z}pra gente, o ouro tem pouco valor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra ser mais específico...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{only this stone. - OG}nós protegíamos esta pedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma escrita?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Writings of history. - OG}Um registro histórico.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É conhecido como um poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can't read it, either. - OG}Nem nós conseguimos ler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:04.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You mean your ancestors\Ndidn't write this? - OG}Quer dizer que isso não foi escrito\Npelos seus ancestrais?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All we know for certain... - OG}Nós sabemos uma coisa com certeza:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:12.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is that this city of Shandora fought and fell trying to protect this stone. - OG}Shandora caiu durante uma batalha\Ndesesperada para proteger esta pedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:17.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We must continue to protect it\Nwith that amount of resolve. - OG}Devemos continuar a protegê-la\Ncom a mesma determinação.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As descendants - OG}Como descendentes deles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:23.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it is our duty to protect\Nthe proof that our ancestors fought and survived. - OG}devemos proteger o legado pelo qual\Nnossos ancestrais arriscaram suas vidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We revere our ancestors\Nas if they were gods. - OG}Reverenciamos nossos antepassados\Ncomo se fossem deuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:33.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Still, I had no idea it was\Nthis giant, gold bell I had heard... - OG}{\q2}Quem diria que era o som\Nde um sino dourado tão enorme...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This bell's ringing has words to it. - OG}Esse som carrega uma mensagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Words? - OG}Uma mensagem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:44.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So that the spirits of our ancestors who were greeted by the heavens - OG}É para os nossos ancestrais que\Nforam acolhidos pelos céus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:49.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{can return to this land at any time without getting lost, - OG}Para que possam ser sempre guiados\Nde volta para esta terra,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we continue to ring this bell, as a way to say, - OG}nós continuamos a tocar este sino,\Ncomo forma de dizer:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:56.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Nós estamos aqui."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:02.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Its sound proclaims the unquestionable glory Shandia once had, - OG}Seu som proclama a inegável\Nglória do passado de Shandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e faz sua existência ser conhecida\Naté os confins do mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós nunca vamos fugir ou nos esconder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:14.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É por isso que chamamos o grande\Nsino desta cidade de "Luz de Shandora."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That explains why it has such a majestic sound! - OG}Um nome digno para\Ncombinar com seu som majestoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você acha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:26.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This light reached out to us and helped us arrive here. - OG}{The light reached out and guided us\Nthrough the storm to get here. - CB}Naquele dia, a luz nos abraçou\Ne nos guiou até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:35.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I heard this bell in a storm where it shouldn't have been audible... - OG}{It should have been inaudible through\Nthe storm. Yet, I heard this bell. - PP}No meio de uma tempestade ensurdecedora,\Neu ouvi o som deste mesmo sino.
Comment: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,851)}I heard this bell in a storm where it shouldn't have been audible...
Comment: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I heard this bell in a storm where it shouldn't have been audible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You like this bell's sound, too? - OG}Você também gosta do som\Ndeste sino, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:47.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you going to grow up to be like that other giant snake someday? - OG}Será que um dia você vai se tornar\Numa serpente gigante também.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Probably not for a hundred more years! - OG}Vamos ver daqui\Na uns cem anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Fique aqui o quanto\Nquiser, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:07.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the first guests here in the 400 years since Shandia fell! - OG}Shandora não recebe visitantes\Ndesde sua queda há 400 anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I want to treat you with lavish hospitality! - OG}Deixe-me mostrar\Nnossa melhor hospitalidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'd love that! - OG}Eu agradeço.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero coletar plantas\Nda floresta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and I want to see this plague\Nall the way through. - OG}e gostaria de acompanhar\Nessa praga até o fim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:22.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro! Comodoro!
Comment: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Comment: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold on, now. What's with the clothes? - OG}Epa, o que houve com essas roupas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha, olha! Um eternal pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E um mapa, Comodoro! Um mapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:32.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pegamos isso de invasores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This skull shape is definitely this island. - OG}O formato de caveira é\Ndefinitivamente esta ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:41.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O nome "Shandora" significa\N"o olho direito da caveira,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:45.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/fad(0,1985)]which refers to this city's location. - OG}o que aponta para a localização desta cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom, se cuide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certifique-se de que ela descanse bastante!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Doutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Venham ver, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Noland's giving us some weird crops! - OG}Noland disse que vai nos dar\Numas plantações estranhas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:06.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have a greenhouse on our ship,\Nwith all kinds of plant samples. - OG}Tem uma estufa no navio\Ncom todo tipo de espécime de planta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll leave some seeds and sprouts that are suited for your soil. - OG}Vou deixar sementes e brotos\Nque são adequados para o solo de vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is that any good? - OG}É gostoso?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sure is! It's also full of nutrients! - OG}Com certeza! E é rico em nutrientes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos trabalhar duro de novo hoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trabalhar duro fazendo o quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fazendo uma festa de fogueira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why would the doctor and the others do this?! - OG}Por que o doutor e\Nseus amigos fariam isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Chief! Noland and\Nthe others are coming! - OG}Chefe! A tripulação de Noland está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escutem! Não falem sobre a noite passada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They said they are going\Nto set sail in a few days. - OG}Eles disseram que planejam\Nzarpar em poucos dias.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:55.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do not do anything rash! - OG}Garantam que não vão\Nfazer nada precipitado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:59.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I guess we can't understand each other after all! - OG}Eu sabia... Nossos povos nunca\Nvão se entender!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:04.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não importa quão boa seja\Na medicina dele, ele ainda é um assassino de deuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:08.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do they think they're great enough to stomp all over our history?! - OG}{\q2}Eles se acham tão superiores que podem\Npisotear toda a nossa história?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:14.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Controlem seus sentimentos\Ne esperem em silêncio até eles partirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui estão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E aí, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Kalgara está por aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:34.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why is everyone acting so coldly\Nall of a sudden? Where's Kalgara? - OG}Por que essa frieza\Nde repente? Cadê o Kalgara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys are outsiders! - OG}Vocês ainda são forasteiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:41.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kalgara doesn't want\Nto see you anymore! - OG}Kalgara disse que não quer\Nver vocês nunca mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:48.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{When are you gonna leave, anyway?! - OG}Quando é que vocês\Nvão embora, afinal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! - OG}Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:55.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They suddenly seem to hate us now... - OG}Parece que eles nos odeiam\Ndo nada...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hold on, you guys! You can't just start acting like this! - OG}Ei, qual é?! O jeito que vocês estão\Nagindo não faz sentido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/fad(0,1476)]Let's continue our work. - OG}{\fad(0,1476)}Vamos continuar trabalhando.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We still have some forest to inspect. - OG}Ainda não terminamos de inspecionar a floresta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here you are, Kalgara! - OG}Aí está você, Kalgara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland estava te procurando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:19.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I don't want to see his face anymore. - OG}É. Eu não quero\Nver a cara dele de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:24.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I do, I think I might kill him! - OG}Se eu ver, capaz de eu matá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O sino não tocou hoje...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:38.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the first time this's happened in the month we've been here. - OG}Isso não aconteceu no mês\Nque estivemos aqui, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll be finished exploring the forest in two days. - OG}Vamos terminar de inspecionar\Na floresta em dois dias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:50.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Diga à tripulação que zarparemos\Nnovamente em três dias,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:54.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so now's their last chance to enjoy solid ground for a while. - OG}então aproveitem o chão firme\Nenquanto podem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:59.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Commodore... To be honest, I wanna get off this awkward island... - OG}{[/q2]Commodore... if we're no longer welcome\Nhere, why don't we just leave? - CB}Comodoro, pra ser sincero, não\Nparece certo ficar aqui mais tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Only after we've finished our duties! - OG}Temos que terminar o que começamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Get some sleep. - OG}Descansem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Live here, Noland! - OG}Fique aqui, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:11.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I know! Why don't you make Mousse your wife?! - OG}Ah! Por que não toma\NA Mousse como sua esposa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.21,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Não seja bobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.42,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have a family back home, with kids about her age. - OG}Eu tenho uma família em casa,\Nincluindo uma criança da idade dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.55,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho que voltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.39,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kalgara doesn't want\Nto see you anymore! - OG}Kalgara disse que não quer\Nver vocês nunca mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:25.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{When are you gonna leave, anyway?! - OG}Quando é que vocês\Nvão embora, afinal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que você está aí, Kalgara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come out! - OG}Apareça!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't you think this is too one-sided?! - OG}Você não acha que me deve\Numa explicação?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tell me why! - OG}Desembucha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I won't understand unless you tell me! - OG}Eu não leio mentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're going to set sail very soon! - OG}Nós vamos zarpar em breve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero me despedir assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:04.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't show your face around me! - OG}Não apareça na minha frente\Nnunca mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you want your wife\Nto end up a widow?! - OG}Ou precisamos nos separar\Npela morte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The commodore seems sad... - OG}O comodoro parece solitário...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:26.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just after he made such a great friend all the way out here... - OG}E depois de fazer um grande amigo\Ntão longe de casa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nada disso faz sentido!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós zarparemos amanhã\Nbem cedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But the villagers are so bloodthirsty\Nwe can't go near 'em, - OG}Os aldeões estão tão hostis\Nque não podemos chegar perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:41.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{not to mention, the bell didn't ring again today... - OG}Sem falar que o sino também\Nnão tocou hoje...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't show your face around me! - OG}Não apareça na minha frente\Nnunca mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.89,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you want your wife\Nto end up a widow?! - 13:04}Ou precisamos nos separar\Npela morte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:11.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que jeito doloroso de partir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:11.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Doutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mousse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tem um minuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:30.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Botanist, my ass! - OG}Que tipo de botânico faria isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:42.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If these are the victims of your "advancements," - OG}Se estas são as vítimas\Ndo seu tal "progresso,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:46.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,então nunca deveríamos\Nter aceitado vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Kindred trees? - OG}Árvores ancestrais?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:58.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is said that all the spirits of our ancestors who died on this island - OG}Dizem que os espíritos dos nossos\Nancestrais que morreram nesta ilha
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:02.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{are guided to them by the bell so they can settle inside them. - OG}residem dentro delas, guiados\Npelo som do sino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:06.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All of our ancestors who lived on\Nthe island since the age of Shandora - OG}Nossos ancestrais viveram aqui\Ndesde a era de Shandora há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:13.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{watch over us from those sacred, white trees. - OG}{watch over us from\Nthose holy white trees. - CB}Cada um deles vela por nós\Nde dentro daquelas árvores brancas sagradas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Kindred Woods are so truly important to us Shandians - OG}Para nós Shandianos,\Nas árvores ancestrais são tão preciosas
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:31.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that we've protected them as much as we've protected our own lives! - OG}que as protegemos como\Nprotegeríamos nossas próprias vidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And we chopped them all down... - OG}E nós fomos e\Nderrubamos todas elas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The warriors were angry and instantly took up their weapons... - OG}{The warriors were\Nimmediately up in arms... - CB}Os guerreiros ficaram tão furiosos\Nque imediatamente pegaram em armas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.09,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{We must drive them off this island! - OG}Expulsem-nos da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.42,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:53.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but since you had saved so many of the villagers' lives... - OG}...mas devíamos a vocês por salvar\Na vida de tantos aldeões...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So that attitude was anger\Nthey couldn't act on... - OG}{So that attitude was from\Ntheir pent-up anger... - PP}Então eles estavam apenas\Nsegurando a raiva...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if it was just for tree research... - OG}Mesmo que fosse para suas pesquisas...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mesmo que vocês não soubessem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:09.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The villagers' anger won't go away now... - OG}a raiva da aldeia nunca vai diminuir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:12.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So, I thought I would\Nat least ask why... - OG}Então, pensei em ao menos\Nperguntar antes de vocês partirem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{before you left... - OG}Por que vocês fizeram isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.58,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei! Alguém me ajuda com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.96,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coloquem tudo a bordo agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.55,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Certifiquem-se de amarrar tudo direitinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Trees where ancestors' spirits dwell... - OG}Árvores onde os espíritos\Ndos ancestrais deles residem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não fazia ideia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've done something that can never be taken back... - OG}Nunca poderemos desfazer\No que fizemos aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os aldeões têm todo direito de estar furiosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas, Comodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tivemos escolha, já que–
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No excuses! - OG}Não tem desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I only did what satisfied me! - OG}{I did what I thought was right... - PP/Viz}Eu só me preocupei em satisfazer\Nminha própria consciência...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm told... - OG}Me disseram...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que além de proclamar\Na existência da cidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:49.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that bell also served to guide their\Nancestors' spirits to the island. - OG}{\q2}aquele sino também servia para guiar os\Nespíritos dos ancestrais de volta à ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:54.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And we cut down those trees! - OG}E nós derrubamos as próprias\Nárvores que os abrigavam!
Comment: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And we cut down those trees!
Comment: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And we cut down those trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We have no reason to be forgiven! - OG}Eles não têm motivo pra nos perdoar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escutem, todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Eh?!\N– Eh?! - OG}– Hã?!\N– Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Leave all the gold behind?!\N– Leave all the gold behind?! - OG}– Quer que deixemos todo o ouro?!\N– Quer que deixemos todo o ouro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:14.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Noland and his men\Nare preparing to leave. - OG}Noland e seus homens\Nestão se preparando pra zarpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mousse! Onde você estava?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:30.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E se...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What if you knew a single, important tree... - OG}E se vocês soubessem que\Numa única árvore preciosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{was tainted by poison... - OG}estivesse contaminada com um veneno mortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And that its poison would eventually spread into the forest, - OG}e que esse veneno eventualmente\Nse espalharia por toda a floresta,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{affect people, and kill an island?! - OG}depois para o seu povo,\Nmatando a ilha inteira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E se vocês soubessem disso antes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean? - OG}O que você está dizendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se fôssemos nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o que faríamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{with that single, important tree?! - OG}com aquela única árvore preciosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dad! Go quickly and stop them! - OG}{Dad! You must go and stop them! - CB}Papai, corre e pare eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não seja tola!\NVocê sabe o que eles fizeram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we part now, we'll regret it for the rest of our lives! - OG}Se deixarmos as coisas assim,\Nvamos nos arrepender pelo resto das nossas vidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você finalmente fez um amigo tão querido,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e nós Shandianos devemos tanto a eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But we're going to leave them hurt for the rest of their lives! - OG}Deixe-os partir, e a dor deles\Nnunca vai cicatrizar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.79,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente vai soar como uma desculpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:30.21,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{but for the commodore's honor, I must say this. - OG}mas pela honra do comodoro,\Nvou contar mesmo assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquelas árvores de vocês\Njá estavam mortas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! - OG}Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{The true horror of\Nthe Kinetsu plague... - OG}O verdadeiro horror de um surto\Nde febre das árvores...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.39,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{is that it can also infect plant life. - OG}é que ela também infecta a vida vegetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.23,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi porque ele sabia disso
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:48.98,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{that the commodore pleaded with you without regard for his own life. - OG}que o comodoro arriscou\Na própria vida para implorar a vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:53.15,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{From people to forest, forest to people... - OG}De pessoas para floresta,\Nde floresta para pessoas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:58.41,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Several small islands have been destroyed in exactly that way. - OG}É exatamente assim que ela\Ndevasta ilhas pequenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.79,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas não há nada\Npara se preocupar agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.71,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Terminamos de verificar\Na floresta inteira ontem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.88,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry that we cut down your beloved woods - OG}Desculpe, não fazíamos ideia\Nde que as árvores que derrubamos eram preciosas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.96,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{without knowing or explaining... - OG}mas ainda assim deveríamos ter explicado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.09,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It'd probably still be unforgivable even with an explanation, - OG}Bom, não espero que nos perdoem,\Nmesmo com uma explicação...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:20.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,mas um botânico nunca prejudicaria\Numa floresta sem um bom motivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.69,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{The commodore doesn't hate gods and spirits and stuff... - OG}Não é que o comodoro\Nodeie deuses ou espíritos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.86,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,é que ele sempre sabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.61,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,o que é mais importante.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer... eles fizeram isso por nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dad! - OG}Papai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.42,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.17,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Não vá ainda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos pegaram tudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All except one thing... - OG}Nem tudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Quit mopin'! Just forget about it! - OG}Para de ficar triste! Esquece isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! It's time to go! - OG}Certo! É hora de ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone to your positions! - OG}Posições, todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're now heading back to the Kingdom of Lvneel! - OG}Estamos voltando para\No Reino de Lvneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.61,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.98,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've committed such a sin! - OG}Eu cometi um pecado grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:17.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Espere! Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zarpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o sino está tocando?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toquem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.59,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Noland - -san}{! - OG}Nos desculpe, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So Noland and the others can hear it! - OG}{So Noland and his crew can hear it! - PP}Garantam que a tripulação de Noland ouça!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro! Olhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:01.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:22.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Volte de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Noland...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:29.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll be waiting for you here! - OG}Vou estar esperando bem aqui por você!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll keep on ringing the bell! - OG}Vou continuar tocando o sino pra você!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:38.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para que seu navio não se perca\Nno mar quando você voltar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:42.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para que você não perca de vista\Nesta ilha durante uma tempestade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:47.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll ring this bell and wait for you! - OG}Vou tocar o sino e esperar por você!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:02.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's meet again someday for sure! Friend of mine! - OG}Vamos nos encontrar de novo\Num dia... meu querido amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu posso...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,voltar de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course I'll be back! - OG}É claro que eu vou voltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:25.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos encontrar de novo com certeza!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=9}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=12}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
